                <li>Fabric 1: 75% Polyester, 20% Viscose, 5% Elastane</li>
                <li>Fabric 2: 100% Polyester,Lining: 100% Polyester</li>
                <li>Fabric 3: 100% Polyester</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
